data.description: What a great buy in the popular Carol Villa neighborhood. Driving through the neighborhood, one gets the feeling of being in the mountains with its hills and curves and beautiful homes of the hillsides. The two most expensive items to replace in a home is the roof and HVAC system! This home boast a young 3-year-old Heating & A/C system and roof is only 4 years old. There is a beautiful saltwater pool oasis that can be enjoyed as many as eight months out of the year. There is a large, detached workshop that has electricity and has security as well as the home. There is a two-car carport with a storage room the length of the carport! You will want to put this home on your must-see list!
